column17: designed to let your little one sleep safe and secure is this Hauck Disney Baby Dream n Play Mobile \u2013 Pooh Bus Cot. This cot is ideal for use for both boys and girls. In addition to this
column19: thereby making it easy for you to carry it along even while you are set to go on long distance voyages with your baby. With this feature
column20: you could fit the cot easily even into the smallest of car boots. You could also set this cot up at home for convenient usage. Furthermore
column21:
you could also store this Hauck Disney Baby Dream n Play Mobile \u2013 Pooh Bus Cot while not in use as it does not occupy much space.

\r\n

\r\n\tThis cot comprises of a mattress that keeps your little one as comfortable as possible while asleep
column22: without letting your baby feel uneasy. The Hauck Disney Baby Dream n Play Mobile \u2013 Pooh Bus Cot also comprises of two mesh sides and solid ends. In addition to this
column23:
the cot also comes with a two wheeled bottom so that you could move the cot from one place to another effortlessly. There is also a carry bag for easy portability of this cot.\xa0

\r\n

\r\n\tThe cot floor area measures 60 x 120 cm
column24:
accommodating your baby comfortably while in use. One of the highlights of this Hauck Disney Baby Dream n Play Mobile \u2013 Pooh Bus Cot is its eye-catching Winnie the Pooh in Bus Design.
